{
  "stem": "24268.1",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the first time, when finally the Germans marched in, after I came back with my sister, we found out that was the first city, the first [INAUDIBLE], the first Jews killed when they marched in.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's very peculiar, because [INAUDIBLE] street was so narrow.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I don't know why they went particularly to this section.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That was downtown.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Hudna, they called.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they killed 30 Jews.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And one of them-- two of them were from our tenants.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "One was Schwartzman, a young couple, just got married.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the other one was the sister-in-law.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The brother also lived there-- was [?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Alterwein. ?] They had two small children.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So two men that's from our house-- they got killed also.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And later, when they-- we came back, I heard, I think, my grandma-- that before I left of my grandmother, I never seen her crying.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But I think like, she felt that it would be probably the last time I seen her.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Her tears are coming down from the cheek.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I didn't-- I think when you're young, you don't even realize the situation, how dangerous, how serious it is.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And we just-- everything-- you just follow, like a-- didn't-- like a-- they didn't-- nobody realizes something that [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But then we start to hear all kind of stories, which they always hide it from us.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "When we came back, I heard this tragedy.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And grandma, being at by my uncle-- because she had her home, but the situation-- obviously, she came to have-- drink coffee or something.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And one German jumped into the window.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And she got scared.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And she got a heart attack drinking her coffee.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
